  "detailed_description": "The tomb of the very first Magi has been discovered, and with it, whispers of riches and treasures untold. That is, if you can get your hands on the mystical sigils that line the tomb’s walls…<br><br>Pick your party and embark on an unforgettable journey to obtain the Sigil of the Magi!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Skill-based cardslinging combat, with the card rack feature to mitigate RNG<br></li><li> Multiple factions, classes, and card choices make for countless of ways to win<br></li><li> Go on a roguelite adventure by making impactful choices that affect your journey through each of the three game worlds</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/7e7db51eb3fe45000130b34c16bc88b8.poster.avif?t=1706586860\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/7e7db51eb3fe45000130b34c16bc88b8.webm?t=1706586860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/7e7db51eb3fe45000130b34c16bc88b8.mp4?t=1706586860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/6bd59a17f2bdadbbc9b6b24a6741b6a2.poster.avif?t=1706586860\" width=595 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/6bd59a17f2bdadbbc9b6b24a6741b6a2.webm?t=1706586860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Every champion has a unique card deck of active and passive skills. Choose a pre-made faction or mix and match to suit your playstyle. Craft a finely-honed deck and prove yourself worthy to finally wield the Sigil of the Magi!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/c1259c8e04289b034f5b8ddbc3172061.webp?t=1706586860\" width=595 height=60 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Countless decks and ways to win</h2>With unique class-based cards, passive abilities, and multiple unlockable classes, there are plenty of strategic options you can experiment with on every run. Drafting a synergistic deck is key to overcoming challenging encounters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/1d6d7d49aa8664aceb074e36001d551e.poster.avif?t=1706586860\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/1d6d7d49aa8664aceb074e36001d551e.webm?t=1706586860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/1d6d7d49aa8664aceb074e36001d551e.mp4?t=1706586860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Obtain powerful, game-changing relics</h2>The Sigil may be the end goal, but Relics provide all kinds of effects and benefits along your journey, and are not tied to any champion. Relics can affect the entire party and sometimes have prerequisites that must be met before they become effective. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/42d5ef83040ff89d550c5d3494dba6c3.webp?t=1706586860\" width=595 height=60 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer your fate with the card rack</h2>Don’t let RNG ruin your run — store your cards on the card rack, reserving them for use on a future turn. Mitigate bad hands by planning ahead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/03767227d61282660ed1814aaf75d9b9.poster.avif?t=1706586860\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/03767227d61282660ed1814aaf75d9b9.webm?t=1706586860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/03767227d61282660ed1814aaf75d9b9.mp4?t=1706586860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your own path towards the Sigil</h2>Make your way through 3 dynamic worlds full of fateful choices hidden secrets and face challenging bosses at the end of each journey. Choose your path wisely and your party will thrive, not just survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/0c6c7059546944c764faf0357870ce3d.avif?t=1706586860\" width=595 height=221 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The tomb of the very first Magi has been discovered, and with it, whispers of riches and treasures untold. That is, if you can get your hands on the mystical sigils that line the tomb’s walls…<br><br>Pick your party and embark on an unforgettable journey to obtain the Sigil of the Magi!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Skill-based cardslinging combat, with the card rack feature to mitigate RNG<br></li><li> Multiple factions, classes, and card choices make for countless of ways to win<br></li><li> Go on a roguelite adventure by making impactful choices that affect your journey through each of the three game worlds</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/7e7db51eb3fe45000130b34c16bc88b8.poster.avif?t=1706586860\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/7e7db51eb3fe45000130b34c16bc88b8.webm?t=1706586860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/7e7db51eb3fe45000130b34c16bc88b8.mp4?t=1706586860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/6bd59a17f2bdadbbc9b6b24a6741b6a2.poster.avif?t=1706586860\" width=595 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/6bd59a17f2bdadbbc9b6b24a6741b6a2.webm?t=1706586860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Every champion has a unique card deck of active and passive skills. Choose a pre-made faction or mix and match to suit your playstyle. Craft a finely-honed deck and prove yourself worthy to finally wield the Sigil of the Magi!<br><br>